The paper deals with active learning for top-k ranking, which is a problem in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper also discusses the multinomial logit model, which is a popular model in statistics and econometrics. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves theoretical analysis and lower bounds, which suggests that it may belong to cs.CC (Computational Complexity) or cs.IT (Information Theory).
